law.catch_line: Relation of numbering system to federal system.
law.text: The numbering system employed pursuant to this chapter shall be in conformity with the overall system of identification numbering adopted by the appropriate agency of the United States government for motorboats within the United States.
law.history: Created 1960 Ky. Acts ch. 68, Art. VIII, sec. 14, effective March 17, 1960.
